'''Dr. Joan''' is a [[Resident|resident]] [[Pediatrics|pediatrician]] at [[St. Ambrose Hospital]].

==History==
When Charlotte and Cooper attended Jake and Addison's wedding, Dr. Joan came to their house to watch their kids.

==Career==
Dr. Joan is a [[Resident|resident]] at [[St. Ambrose Hospital|St. Ambrose Hospital's]] [[Pediatrics|pediatrics program]].

==Notes and Trivia==
*Although her back is briefly seen in [[In Which We Say Goodbye]], the actress portraying Dr. Joan is uncredited.
